This tool helps search through Craigslist housing (apartments) ads.

INSTALLATION

Clone the repository.
    git clone git://github.com/pwnall/clh.git

This needs the pre-release version of bundler to install Rails edge.
    gem install bundler --pre
    bundle install

Database setup (MySQL needed).
   rake db:migrate
   
Populate the database using the desired housing page from your city.
  script/populator.rb http://boston.craigslist.org/gbs/aap/

Run the server.
  rails s
  
Point your browser to http://localhost:3000 to play.
